elements.name: Como autor creo un post y lo edito

steps.name: I navigate to page "<HOST>" "ghost/#/signin"
I login with credentials "<USERNAME>" "<PASSWORD>"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "logged"
I wait for 2 seconds
I go to new post form
I send a signal to user 2 containing "creating"
I wait for 2 seconds
I create a post with title "$name_1" and content "$string_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "posting"
I wait for 2 seconds
I post the post

steps.name: I send a signal to user 2 containing "post created"
I wait for a signal containing "checking post" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "checked post" for 30 seconds
I return to posts list
I select the listed post with name "$$name_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "editing"
I wait for 2 seconds
I change the post content for "$string_2"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "edited"
I wait for 2 seconds
I update the post
I send a signal to user 2 containing "post edited"

name: Crear un post y que este sea visible para el usuario, editarlo y que el usuario vea las modificaciones
